examples.en: We waited in silence.

examples.en: We were received in silence.

examples.en: He waited in silence until I came across with the truth.
examples.ru: Он молча ждал, пока я не расскажу правду.

examples.en: Silence fell as I entered the room.

examples.en: The audience sat in stunned silence.
